text: Petter Strand (born 24 August 1994) is a Norwegian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Brann. He has previously played for Fyllingsdalen, Sogndal and Molde. ==Career== Strand joined Sogndal in 2014. He made his debut for Sogndal in a 3–0 defeat against Stabæk. On 28 January 2016, Strand joined Molde FK. He made his Molde debut in a 2–1 win against Stabæk on 20 March 2016.
